<div class="postscript">
<p>Directions for the Busts<a class="ptr" href="#GEWN-02-06-02-0189-0002-fn-0076" id="GEWN-02-06-02-0189-0002-fn-0076-ptr">76</a></p>
<p>4one of Alexr the Greatanother of Julius Csaranr of Chs 12 Sweeden &amp; a 4th of the King Prussia.</p>
<p>N.B.these are not to exceed 15 Inchs in hight nor 10 in width for brokn Pedimt.</p>
<p>2 other Busts of Prince Eugene &amp; the Duke Of Marlborhsomewht smallr. 2 Wild Beastsnot to exceed 12 Inch in highth nor18 in length. Sundry Small Ornaments for Chim[ne]y piece.<a class="ptr" href="#GEWN-02-06-02-0189-0002-fn-0077" id="GEWN-02-06-02-0189-0002-fn-0077-ptr">77</a></p>
</div>
